## Dotfile Management

These instructions are managed by **chezmoi**. The file you are reading is a rendered artifact — never edit it directly. Chezmoi will overwrite any direct changes on the next `apply`.

**Source of truth:** `~/.local/share/chezmoi/`

| What | Source path |
|---|---|
| Shared rules | `.chezmoitemplates/<name>` |
| Claude entry point | `dot_claude/CLAUDE.md.tmpl` |
| Claude commands | `dot_claude/commands/*.md.tmpl` |
| Gemini entry point | `dot_gemini/GEMINI.md.tmpl` |
| Gemini commands | `dot_gemini/commands/*.toml.tmpl` |
| Chezmoi config | `.chezmoi.toml.tmpl` |

To edit a shared rule, update `.chezmoitemplates/<name>`, then run `chezmoi apply`.
